! Body Part Diagram Editor

Developer tool for generating and refining body-region-* meta fields from an anatomical source image.

1. Open <$link to="$:/plugins/linonetwo/body-part-diagram-editor/pages/BodyPartDiagramEditor">the editor page</$link>.
2. Click Generate Regions to rebuild polygons from the source image alpha mask.
3. Drag handles for local fixes, then save the result back into the image meta tiddler.